| 1. Before you Hit Level One...                                              |
+=============================================================================+

Itinerary:  Pick up 3 hearts, the White Sword, the Letter, the Blue Candle, the
            Magic Shield and the Blue Ring

HEART 1:
  * Get the wooden sword in the cave.

  * Head right 8 screens (half the length of Hyrule) until you reach the sea,
    killing everything and getting money.  If you also get bombs from the 
    enemies then you can skip the next step.

  * Go up one screen, into the cave, and buy -=BOMBS=- (20 rupees)

  * Go down and then left 4 screens.  There is a path to the north here, place
    your bomb on the wall to the left of the path, the 2nd tile from the right.

