HEART 2:
  * Head north 5 screens (or until you can't go north anymore)

  * Go right 1 screen.  There is a big rock in the center of the screen.  Bomb
    the rock again 2nd from the right side.  (note: notice the diagonal rocks
    by on the edge of the big rock, those can't ever be bombed, but they still
